      <title>随着收入下降，加州赤字增加 150 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/california-deficit-seen-rising-by-15-billion-as-revenue-drops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州预算顾问表示，由于新数据显示税收收入低于之前的估计，该州的赤字可能会增加 26%，达到 730 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/california-deficit-seen-rising-by-15-billion-as-revenue-drops</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 21:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
